{"tid":2192781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★廢老：HK is福地！新推4居屋3望墳景 呎價或逾萬","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:45:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d803d598ca13973cfde23fec6a81a687e817c83","tid":2192781,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:40:54.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】新一期居屋將於下周四（10日）開始接受申請，房委會昨於網站公布4個新居屋屋苑資料。鑽石山啟翔苑為今期唯一坐落市區的屋苑，價格亦最高，以臨時市值折扣率六三折計，部分單位呎價逾萬元。由於附近道路繁忙，近馬路單位設隔音鰭或有礙景觀；馬鞍山錦駿苑則有居屋少見的隔音露台。另3個非市區屋苑部分單位均有可能望到墳景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200904/s00002/1599157183687/%e6%96%b0%e6%8e%a84%e5%b1%85%e5%b1%8b3%e6%9c%9b%e5%a2%b3%e6%99%af-%e5%95%9f%e7%bf%94%e8%8b%91%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b9%e6%88%96%e9%80%be%e8%90%ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200904%2Fs00002%2F1599157183687%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%258e%25a84%25e5%25b1%2585%25e5%25b1%258b3%25e6%259c%259b%25e5%25a2%25b3%25e6%2599%25af-%25e5%2595%259f%25e7%25bf%2594%25e8%258b%2591%25e5%2591%258e%25e5%2583%25b9%25e6%2588%2596%25e9%2580%25be%25e8%2590%25ac&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=1c8aea25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200904%2Fs00002%2F1599157183687%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%258e%25a84%25e5%25b1%2585%25e5%25b1%258b3%25e6%259c%259b%25e5%25a2%25b3%25e6%2599%25af-%25e5%2595%259f%25e7%25bf%2594%25e8%258b%2591%25e5%2591%258e%25e5%2583%25b9%25e6%2588%2596%25e9%2580%25be%25e8%2590%25ac&h=8002c885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200904/s00002/1599157183687/%e6%96%b0%e6%8e%a84%e5%b1%85%e5%b1%8b3%e6%9c%9b%e5%a2%b3%e6%99%af-%e5%95%9f%e7%bf%94%e8%8b%91%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b9%e6%88%96%e9%80%be%e8%90%ac</a>"},{"pid":"38cc28a7bc121517b6dfa4ccca869d002a5e011a","tid":2192781,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike